<div class="white-box">
    <div class="turquoise-box">
    </div>
    <br><br><h3>Create a budget plan for your next trip</h3><br><br><br><br><br><br>

    <p class="new-trip-text">
        Create your new trip to keep track of spending. <br><br>
        Put in your information below and we will help you to keep track of your budget as you travel. <br><br>
        We will let you know when you have blown it and when you have cash to splash. <br><br><br><br><br>
    </p>

    <div class="all-form-padding">
        <form class="form-group all-forms new-trip-form" data-remote="true" >
            <h4 align="center">Make a budget for your upcoming trip to keep track of your spending</h4><br>
            <label for="name">What do you want to name your upcoming trip?</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="trip-name" >
            <br><label for="budget-total">What is the total budget of your trip in USD?</label>
            <input type="number" class="form-control" id="budget-total" placeholder="eg. 2400" >
            <br><label for="length-total">What is the start date of your trip?</label>
            <input type="date" class="form-control" id="start-date" >
            <br><label for="length-total">What is the end date of your trip?</label>
            <input type="date" class="form-control" id="end-date" >
            <br><button type="submit" id="new-trip-submit" class="all-form-buttons">Create my new budget</button>
            <button type="reset" id="welcome-reset" class="all-form-buttons">Reset</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>